WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Welcome to British English Academy A1-M09: Problems, solutions and critical thinking. Learners practise speak in rehearsed exchanges through cause/effect, evidence, debate, solutions. The teacher models past simple of be, introduces vocabulary such as environment, social issues, cause/effect, solution language, then learners complete quiz, evidence upload and reflection.
